(11, '43) The CREATE TRIGGER statement is used to create the trigger. The _____ clause specifies the table name on which the trigger is to be attached. The ______ specifies that this is an AFTER INSERT trigger. ', 'a. For insert, on', 'b. On, for insert', 'c. For, insert', 'd. Both a and c', 'b', 'Not Avavilable'),
