(11, '62) The HAVING clause does which of the following?', 'a. Acts like a WHERE clause but is used for groups rather than rows.', 'b. Acts like a WHERE clause but is used for rows rather than columns.', 'c. Acts like a WHERE clause but is used for columns rather than groups.', 'd. Acts EXACTLY like a WHERE clause.', 'a', 'Not Avavilable'),
