(11, '87) Which of the following code will remove all the rows from the table LOCATIONS?', 'a. DROP TABLE locations;', 'b. DELETE TABLE locations;', 'c. TRUNCATE TABLE locations;', 'd. None of the above.', 'c', 'Not Avavilable'),
